        <div style="width: 50%; background-color:#00AEEF; color:white; text-align:center; padding: 5px; border-radius: 10px;">
            <h1>Welcome to अमृतम</h1>
            <p style="color:white">
                A sanctuary of tradition, purity, and wellness. Our commitment to crafting exceptional A2 Gir Cow Ghee
