    <section id="about">
        <div class="about-section">
            <div class="about-row">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="/Picture/1.png" alt="Our Story">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text" style="background-color:#00AEEF;color:white">
                    <h2 style="text-align:center">Our Story</h2>
                    <p style="color:white">Amrutam's roots trace back to a profound respect for time-honored dairy practices. A spark of inspiration ignited our founders' desire to share these invaluable benefits with a wider audience. Thus, Gaayam was born, a haven where the qualities of A2 Gir Cow Ghee and the significance of Gir cows merge seamlessly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-row reverse">
                <div class="about-text" style="background-color:#00AEEF;color:white">
                    <h2 style="text-align:center">Our Mission and Values</h2>
                    <p style="color:white">At Amrutam, our mission is clear: to provide you with the purest A2 Gir Cow Ghee while preserving the essence of traditional dairy practices. Our values are the pillars that guide us: authenticity, quality, tradition, health, sustainability, and community engagement. Every step we take is rooted in these principles, ensuring that the products you experience embody the finest standards and cherished heritage.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="/Picture/2.png" alt="Our Mission and Values">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-row">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="/Picture/3.png" alt="Our Vision for the Future">
                </div>
                <div class="about-text" style="background-color:#00AEEF;color:white">
                    <h2 style="text-align:center">Our Vision for the Future</h2>
                    <p style="color:white">Our vision extends far beyond the present. Amrutam aspires to grow, innovate, and make a positive impact on both your well-being and the world around you. We envision expanding our offerings, igniting educational initiatives, and fostering community connections. Together, we're creating a legacy that celebrates tradition while embracing the possibilities of the future.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

